  "text": "and a true solution u(x, t) of (1.2), on sufficiently long time scales. In [CITATION_1] this has been achieved for a variety of cases using a separation of the critical mode (the phase mode) from the exponentially damped remaining modes by Bloch wave analysis. Here, for special initial data we obtain the diffusive stability results and the mixing results from Theorems 1 and 2. The proofs heavily rely on the coordinates from [CITATION_2] , which are introduced in §3. ",
